The below will be used through the Postman for checking the status of the Oracle DB connector i.e., "oracle-sink" as a "GET" method in the Postman 
URL = "http://localhost:8083/connectors/oracle-sink/status"


The status of the whole "oracle-sink" connector will be checked through the following URL only "http://localhost:8083/connectors/oracle-sink/status" by hitting it on the Postman
